They used prerecord for the first time this comeback, JK was lip syncing the majority of his part. Look at V on "rain keep pouring" part. He missed the "rain keep".
Not saying they can't sing at all, just saying they are humans too, and singing that clear with dance THAT intense is simply impossible. No one can do that, even BTS.
Glad they made the prerecord though, it sounds way better then just studio version (which they used till this comeback on all Korean comeback stages)
